channel.title: Misthalin - Great Runescape Guide Site
channel.description:
[b][center]Misthalin[/center][/b] Misthalin is a farely new Runescape Fan/Tip site. We have been working on getting guides for members ever since it started. We already have all Free to play quests and some Members quests submitted and a few city guides. I highly recomend you going to Misthalin becasue we have a great community and everyone is nice. So please check out www.misthalin.com look at the guides if you need help and be sure to register at the forums we have arcades and alot more. Also at the forums we have way more submissions of other Runescape stuff.
Remember [url=http://misthalin.com]misthalin.com[/url] look at the guides and register at the forums :) And the forums are [url=http://www.misthalin.com/forum]www.misthalin.com/forum[/url]
Feel free to give us suggestions and compliments. But please dont flame me...
[center]I do have permission to post this.[/center]
